{"tid":309273,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個你曾經遇過奇怪又解釋唔到既事","createTime":"2017-07-05T01:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T06:50:58.000Z","uid":102335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0920ea7624d178d4be32919d7872e5ce9f2f7d4f","tid":309273,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:18:30.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n我細個既時候住係好舊既井字型樓<br />\n個時呀媽拖我落街食野<br />\n搭lift時係10樓停左<br />\n有一個同我老豆個樣一模一樣既人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係直頭同我舊屋掛住我老豆後生既look既衫一樣<br />\n個時我feel到我媽拖得我好實<br />\n到地下一出lift我呀媽拖住我走得勁快<br />\n個時冇問過 到大個左都冇問過 因為都幾驚下<br />\n<br />\n利申：個時我老豆仲在生既同我老豆冇孖生既"},{"pid":"1c09988e6e06c95c27f89e4b739e269233ecc5dd","tid":309273,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先<br />\n<br />\n我細個既時候住係好舊既井字型樓<br />\n個時呀媽拖我落街食野<br />\n搭lift時係10樓停左<br />\n有一個同我老豆個樣一模一樣既人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係直頭同我舊屋掛住我老豆後生既look既<span style=\"color: red;\">相</span>一樣<br />\n個時我feel到我媽拖得我好實<br />\n到地下一出lift我呀媽拖住我走得勁快<br />\n個時冇問過 到大個左都冇問過 因為都幾驚下<br />\n<br />\n利申：個時我老豆仲在生既同我老豆冇孖生既</blockquote>"},{"pid":"885b30b34dbabe10ad70fc139c9c26d4d0dffc59","tid":309273,"uid":55614,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:21:28.000Z","msg":"人有相似姐<br />\n屋村打扮個個都咁上下"},{"pid":"895cd055d73c1d6b3957eed372c06c2d9a2f0d74","tid":309273,"uid":70163,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:22:15.000Z","msg":"第一 可能眼花<br />\n<br />\n第二 細過會容易見鬼，佢可能想搵你啊爸做替身，想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d55e4ab6716d9c4ebd2f7571fd3fec4fd1fa5b","tid":309273,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:26:12.000Z","msg":"你老豆仲在生 見到佢有咩解釋唔到<br />\n<br />\n定係你講緊見到個同你老豆20年前個樣一樣既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9a15346b74a0246dc79e607144aec4f1a0c06f","tid":309273,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一 可能眼花<br />\n<br />\n第二 細過會容易見鬼，佢可能想搵你啊爸做替身，想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人想知"},{"pid":"5214ed9299f3f55393351bcc0f01f2e9a24a9604","tid":309273,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆仲在生 見到佢有咩解釋唔到<br />\n<br />\n定係你講緊見到個同你老豆20年前個樣一樣既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我表達得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時我呀爸係返緊工 所以唔可能係佢<br />\n我個時見到既係同我老豆20年前個樣一樣既人<br />\n直頭個look都一樣"},{"pid":"a1edb01078e10e3199b96fb5081f19a8defa6c54","tid":309273,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你老豆仲在生 見到佢有咩解釋唔到<br />\n<br />\n定係你講緊見到個同你老豆20年前個樣一樣既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我表達得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時我呀爸係返緊工 所以唔可能係佢<br />\n我個時見到既係同我老豆20年前個樣一樣既人<br />\n直頭個look都一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋我老豆老左頭髮唔多<br />\n但個時見到好似我老豆個個人頭髮好多<br />\n同我屋企掛呀爸後生既相個髮型一樣"},{"pid":"32cba534d26c2a16240edc2be4f7e277d2044f43","tid":309273,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先<br />\n<br />\n我細個既時候住係好舊既井字型樓<br />\n個時呀媽拖我落街食野<br />\n搭lift時係10樓停左<br />\n有一個同我老豆個樣一模一樣既人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係直頭同我舊屋掛住我老豆後生既look既衫一樣<br />\n個時我feel到我媽拖得我好實<br />\n到地下一出lift我呀媽拖住我走得勁快<br />\n個時冇問過 到大個左都冇問過 因為都幾驚下<br />\n<br />\n利申：個時我老豆仲在生既同我老豆冇孖生既</blockquote><br />\n呀媽：<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事既</span>，呀仔。"},{"pid":"5c63a4b769d9d1bc0a8a2dcf9bce693e3f5a4d1e","tid":309273,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我先<br />\n<br />\n我細個既時候住係好舊既井字型樓<br />\n個時呀媽拖我落街食野<br />\n搭lift時係10樓停左<br />\n有一個同我老豆個樣一模一樣既人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係直頭同我舊屋掛住我老豆後生既look既衫一樣<br />\n個時我feel到我媽拖得我好實<br />\n到地下一出lift我呀媽拖住我走得勁快<br />\n個時冇問過 到大個左都冇問過 因為都幾驚下<br />\n<br />\n利申：個時我老豆仲在生既同我老豆冇孖生既</blockquote><br />\n呀媽：<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事既</span>，呀仔。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老豆係個種絕世好爸爸<br />\n<br />\n有冇人講下奇怪又解釋唔既事？"},{"pid":"6238ee63723958ac56f3cbcc956fe2cc78e66b73","tid":309273,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"聽人講見到一個一模一樣嘅人個真身會好快死"},{"pid":"7b25db3eb56e96d568034fb4b24d73821ad20f18","tid":309273,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"你唔問返你阿媽"},{"pid":"54874a3eb150d5ee9ff996528209324d9679b986","tid":309273,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽人講見到一個一模一樣嘅人個真身會好快死</blockquote><br />\n我聽講係自己見到自己先會"},{"pid":"a2429af2bfb4cfd8678a641b63ca396296ef8ea7","tid":309273,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔問返你阿媽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個唔敢問 以家問應該會話唔記得<br />\n不過都唔會問 因為我老豆唔係到已一年<br />\n廢事佢傷心"},{"pid":"8cc3c0aa87b490a1da0c75507d98af6b049ec015","tid":309273,"uid":122537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:33:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講多啲,好似幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c05bf930c08380a63a79de68b8ed15c5b7c90","tid":309273,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"向京都入住既町家發生，部 bose 音響 play 音樂時無端端自已會較到最大 volume，之後一日機已熄既情況下出街直至黃昏返去入屋時發現呢張 message。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/KYOTO%202015/9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2FKYOTO%25202015%2F9496C266-A366-4321-BCE0-C8ED0A131E90.jpg&h=706457ff&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}